可以設置中斷點，方便程式除錯。 launch.json In VSCode: Exploer -> New Folder 輸入 .vscode new folder icon In VSCode: Exploer -> New File 輸入 launch.json 在文字輸入區輸入以下設定檔 { "version": "0.2.0", "configurations": [ { "name": "(gdb) Launch", "type": "cppdbg", "request": "launch", "program": "${workspaceFolder}/a.out", "args": [], "stopAtEntry": false, "cwd": "${workspaceFolder}", "environment": [], "externalConsole": false, "MIMode": "gdb", "setupCommands": [ { "description": "Enable pretty-printing for gdb", "text": "-enable-pretty-printing", "ignoreFailures": true } ] } ]
} 編譯 & 執行 Debugger In VSCode Terminal: $ g++ -g test.cpp
